<div>
<h1>How do I access a shared folder on my home server from KyBook 3?</h1>
<p>With KyBook 2 I was able to access a share folder on my home server through WiFi to add books. I don't see that option in KyBook 3.</p>
<p>The option is there. On the home screen:</p>
<ol>
<li>Tap the big red <code>Add</code> button (see image below)</li>
<li>Tap <code>Folder</code></li>
<li>Tap <code>Add SMB/CIFS Share</code></li>
</ol

<h3>Note that you may find <code>Add SMB/CIFS Share</code> under <code>File Browser</code> on an iPad.</h3>
</div>
